wiki.content: "Classy 101" is a reggaeton song by Colombian singer Feid and Puerto Rican rapper and singer Young Miko. It was published as a single on March 30, 2023 through Universal Music Latino. The track is a modern reggaeton penned by Feid, Young Miko, Caleb Calloway, Miguel Montoya, and other songwriters; and was produced by Calloway, Julia Lewis and Mauro. The lyrics deal explicitly with a carnal desire linked to lust and sexual satisfaction, in which it speaks of a figure that is provocative, which distances itself from the most romantic aspects and immerses itself in a game of hot attraction.
